# Implementation Docs Priority

When assisting with this repository, always consult and follow these documents before implementing changes:

- `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`
- `docs/DATABASE_SCHEMA.md`
- `docs/MODULE_IO.md`

Rules:

- Do not introduce code that contradicts those documents.
- If code and docs diverge, update code and docs together in the same change.
- For new modules, add/update I/O contracts in `docs/MODULE_IO.md`.
- For schema changes, update `docs/DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` and matching Alembic migration.
- For flow/state changes, update `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` accordingly.
